window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Allen Ming awakens in an unfamiliar realm, trapped within an unfamiliar formâ€”feeble in body and spirit.</p> <p>Thrust into a world of cultivation, Allen Ming finds himself grappling with a reality of a wastrel body, and a world filled with danger and killing.</p> <p>With an AI-enhanced eye, he seeks his way through the dark world of cultivation. But with his newfound family haunted by a looming threat, he has to take charge of the situation even before he gets familiar with the new body.</p> <p>Embark on a journey with Allen Ming as he walks on the path of immortality with the help of AI System and character sheets.</p>"; 
